name: Exploding Mosaics IV: Dogecoin to $1 (3/4)
description: Such boom. Much cool. Watch this Dogecoin Mosaic explode and turn into a $1 coin (a reassembled "$1" mosaic merging with the faded Dogecoin in the background). There are 2 Limited Editions of this coin (with glistening effects): one minted on OpenSea and one on HEN. There are 4 Regular Editions minted: 2 on OpenSea and 2 on HEN. This piece is the Regular Edition. The first two of the Regular Editions are minted on OpenSea.
